### Get a Patient by ID
GET https://hapi.fhir.org/baseR4/Patient/12345
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### Search Patients by name
GET https://hapi.fhir.org/baseR4/Patient?name=Smith?gender=male
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### Create a new Patient
POST https://hapi.fhir.org/baseR4/Patient
Content-Type: application/fhir+json
Accept: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Patient",
  "name": [
    {
      "family": "Doe",
      "given": ["Jane"]
    }
  ],
  "gender": "female",
  "birthDate": "1985-03-15"
}

###

### Update an existing Patient
PUT https://hapi.fhir.org/baseR4/Patient/12345
Content-Type: application/fhir+json
Accept: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Patient",
  "id": "12345",
  "name": [
    {
      "family": "Doe",
      "given": ["Jane", "Marie"]
    }
  ],
  "gender": "female",
  "birthDate": "1985-03-15"
}

###

### Delete a Patient by ID
DELETE https://hapi.fhir.org/baseR4/Patient/12345
Accept: application/fhir+json
